description: Vans has been a go-to for skaters and sneakerheads since 1966, and the Old Skool silhouette is a testament to the brand's legacy. This 'Gum Block' colorway offers a fresh take on a classic, with an archival checkerboard motif over the canvas upper overlaid by premium suede and a leather logo panel. description: Looking for a pair of shoes that are as unique as you are? Check out the Vans Sk8 Hi in Triple Black. This high-top shoe is made with a suede upper and comes in a sleek, all-black finish. It also features a leather side-stripe, foxing stripe, and rubber midsole for added style and durability. The woven tongue tag and rubber license plate at the heel add a pop of color to this otherwise stealthy shoe. And for ultimate comfort, the Sk8 Hi is equipped with Vans’ signature waffle outsole. So whether you’re hitting the skate park or just cruising around town, do it in style with the Vans Sk8 Hi.

description:
Who says you can't reach for the stars? With these Vans NASA x Old Skool 'Space Voyager' shoes, you can feel like an astronaut without leaving the ground. These stylish sneakers are perfect for those who want to show their love of space exploration.
The white leather upper and NASA logo on the quarter panel are eye-catching and immediately convey the theme of the shoe. The exposed foam around the collar and Velcro American flag patch at the heel add a unique touch that is inspired by old space suits.

The classic Vans side stripe adds a touch of nostalgia to the shoe, and the overall design makes this sneaker a must-have for any skater.

The cushioned collar improves comfort and mobility, and the autoclave sole provides signature Vans style. With its unique design and casual style, the Vans Old Skool 'Blur Check' sneaker is perfect for everyday wear.

The Slip-On also features a padded collar and signature rubber waffle outsole for ultimate comfort and protection.

The paisley prints on the upper are contrasted by a white rubber midsole with a black foxing stripe. A yellow waffle-traction rubber outsole provides grip and traction. This sneaker is perfect for those who want to stand out from the crowd.

Mismatched textiles sourced from American-made bandanas are featured on each sneaker’s medial side, while navy suede paneling can be found at the vamp, heel and eyestay. A solid white rubber midsole with red accents on the foxing stripe and license plate completes the look.

title: Vans DSM x Old Skool 'DSM Check'  VN0004OJJ7L
description: The Vans DSM x Old Skool 'DSM Check' is a must-have sneaker for any casual or streetwear enthusiast. This unique take on the classic Old Skool features a black and white checkerboard canvas upper with Dover Street Market branding placed throughout. The sneaker also sports black suede accents on the toe box, heel, and eyestay, as well as a white leather side stripe and red Vans branding on the midsole. Whether you're hitting the streets or just kicking back, the Vans DSM x Old Skool 'DSM Check' is a great sneaker to add to your rotation.

title: Vans MoMA x ComfyCush Old Skool 'Colorful Checkerboard'  VN0A3WMA1PJ
description: The Vans MoMA Comfycush Old Skool ‘Colorful Checkerboard’ is a shoe that is both stylish and comfortable. The canvas upper is lined with moisture-wicking materials, and the iconic checkerboard pattern has been given a multicolored twist. The lateral side panel is inscribed with ‘MoMA’ in oversized lettering, making this a perfect shoe for art lovers. The ComfyCush midsole provides cushioning and support, making this shoe ideal for everyday wear.

The vulcanized sole and rubber outsole provide excellent traction and durability, while the canvas and suede upper offer a comfortable fit.

The Supreme x Classic Slip-On Pro 'Diamond Plate Yellow' is a low-cut canvas upper with 'Supreme' branding on the lateral. A vulcanized sole with rubber Waffle tread provides a classic feel.

The upper is made from suede and canvas, with a Diamond Plate print that is inspired by slip-resistant steel plating. 'Supreme' lettering on the sidewall ensures that everyone knows you're wearing the latest collaboration between Vans and NY skate and fashion brand, Supreme. The vulcanized sole provides lasting comfort, while the Waffle tread offers excellent grip.

title: Vans Comme des Garçons x Authentic 'CDG'  VN0A33TASHM
description: The Vans Comme des Garcons x Authentic CDG is a limited edition sneaker released in 2018 in collaboration with Comme des Garçons. The sneaker features a white canvas upper with “CDG” printed all over. The low top also sports rubberized black CDG lettering on the toe box, white laces, a white leather collar lining, and a white cupsole with a black outsole. This sneaker is perfect for those who are looking for something unique and different to add to their collection.

title: Vans Comme des Garçons x Authentic LX 'Graffiti'  VN0A33TAKXY
description: The Vans Comme des Garcons x Authentic LX sneaker is the perfect shoe for those who appreciate individuality and self-government. This edition's white canvas upper is covered in graffiti-style slogans including 'My energy comes from freedom' and 'Live free with a strong will', representing these values perfectly. Metal eyelets and a tone-on-tone heel patch return classic style, while the vulcanized rubber with matching foxing tape and gum Waffle tread finish it off. Whether you're hitting the streets or the skate park, this shoe is sure to make a statement.

title: Vans Disney x Old Skool 'Mickey'  VN0A38G1UNC
description: Introducing the Vans Disney x Old Skool 'Mickey'! For Mickey Mouse's 90th anniversary, Vans has teamed up with Disney to release exclusive colorways for adults and children alike. This low top features an all-white canvas upper with the classic white leather stripe on the side. The padded collar ensures comfort, while the Mickey Mouse head in black on the tongue and large Mickey hand coming out of the heel add a touch of fun and whimsy.

title: Vans Disney x Slip-On 'Mickey & Minnie'  VN0A38F7UJ4
description: Celebrate the 90th anniversary of Mickey Mouse with the Vans Disney x Slip-On 'Mickey & Minnie' shoes. These special edition shoes feature a black and white checkerboard upper, side panel flames, a padded collar, and a large Mickey Mouse head printed on the toe box. The vulcanized outsole provides flexibility and superior traction, making these shoes perfect for any activity.

title: Vans Disney x Old Skool 'Mickey Mouse Club'  VN0A38G1UNB
description: Introducing the Vans Disney x Old Skool 'Mickey Mouse Club'! Part of a special collaboration between Vans and Disney to celebrate Mickey Mouse's 90th birthday, this Old Skool sneaker is rendered in black suede and canvas with a red jazz stripe. Mickey Mouse himself is embroidered in yellow on the heels, with a cartoon hidden tribute on the interior. The tongue logo also features Mickey for an extra touch of fun.

title: Vans Supreme x Sid Pro 'White Dalmatian'  VN0A3XTISJP
description: Looking for a unique twist on a classic Vans silhouette? Check out the Supreme x Sid Pro 'White Dalmatian.' This streetwear-ready low top first debuted in 1995, and was brought back in 2018 via a four-sneaker collab with Supreme. The 'White Dalmatian' is the only one of the four that features a graphic, with a white suede upper speckled with black dots. You'll find Supreme branding on the tongue and OG Vans branding on the side, along with twin piping on the vulcanized midsole for a premium finish.

title: Vans Disney x SK8-HI 'Mickey & Minnie'  VN0A38GEUPN
description: Introducing the Vans Disney x Sk8-Hi 'Mickey & Minnie'! This women's-exclusive sneaker is perfect for any fan of the classic cartoon characters. Mickey Mouse is featured on the right shoe, greeting his girlfriend Minnie Mouse with flowers. On the left shoe, a series of flower embroideries adds a feminine touch. The rest of the shoe is designed with a pink suede and canvas upper, making it super soft and comfortable to wear. Special-edition packaging incorporates Vans' checkerboard motif with a heritage graphic of Mickey, making this sneaker truly unique.

description: If you're looking for a shoe that seamlessly blends style and function, then you need the Vans Supreme x Sid Pro. This low-top shoe is perfect for both skateboarding and everyday wear, thanks to its versatile black suede upper and thick white midsole. The retro Vans logo on the quarter panel gives the shoe a touch of nostalgia, while the Old English Supreme branding across the tongue adds a bit of street cred.

The sneaker features a red and white polka-dot design on the canvas upper, with Minnie's signature bow in place of laces. The interior of the shoe is stamped with classic Mickey cartoons for a unique look. The sneakers come in their own special-edition packaging, making them the perfect gift for any Disney fan.

title: Vans Old Skool 'Logo Mix'  VN0A38G1UA9
description: Looking for a classic silhouette with a modern twist? Look no further than the Vans Old Skool 'Logo Mix' sneaker. This retro-inspired shoe takes the best of the 1977 original and adds a fewemporary details to give it a unique edge. The iconic logos and branding are repeated throughout the canvas upper, while the white sidestripe provides a pop of contrast. The interior is lightly padded for comfort, and the vulcanized gum rubber outsole gives you lasting wear.

title: Vans Fear of God x Era 95 Reissue 'Marshmallow'  VN0A2XRYML6
description: The Vans Fear of God x Era 95 Reissue 'Marshmallow' shoe is a must-have for any fashion-savvy individual. This limited-edition design commemorates the 50th anniversary of the Vans Era silhouette with a sleek, Off-White upper adorned with black Fear of God logos. The era 95 reissue provides excellent support and comfort with its vulcanized construction and rubber outsole, making it perfect for everyday wear.

title: Vans Disney x Taka Hayashi x SK8-HI 'Mickey's 90th'  VN0A3WNDRNR
description: To celebrate Mickey Mouse's 90th anniversary, Vans teamed up with renowned artist Taka Hayashi to create a special edition Disney x Taka Hayashi x Sk8-Hi sneaker. This sneaker is covered in various shades of blue denim, with alternating Mickey-inspired patches at the ankle that depict a cactus and hot air balloon. The vulcanized rubber midsole and gum outsole keep the look classic, while the addition of these special details make this sneaker a must-have for any Disney or Vans fan.

title: Vans Disney x Geoff McFetridge x SK8-HI 'Mickey's 90th'  VN0A38FYRNQ
description: To celebrate Mickey Mouse's 90th anniversary, Vans has teamed up with LA-based artist Geoff McFetridge to create an exclusive line of sneakers. The Vans Disney x Geoff McFetridge x Sk8-Hi sneaker is a stylish take on the classic Sk8-Hi silhouette, with a high-top canvas upper covered in an elegant line-drawn Mickey print. Off-White suede overlays add a touch of luxury to the eyestay and heel, while a vulcanized midsole with rubber outsole provides comfort and grip.

title: Vans SK8-Hi Reissue 'Japanese Type'  VN0A2XSBSJZ
description: Vans is excited to introduce the Vans Sk8-Hi Reissue 'Japanese Type' sneaker. This iconic 1978 silhouette has been updated with Japanese street style and California skate culture in mind. The shoe features a canvas and suede upper in a monochromatic color scheme. 'Vans' is embroidered in bold Japanese Katakana typography at the ankle, with an 'Off The Wall' bumper logo at the heel. The vulcanized midsole provides cushioning and support, while the waffle outsole gives you signature Vans traction.

description: To celebrate the 50th anniversary of Led Zeppelin's self-titled debut album, Vans has released a special edition SK8-Hi. This high-top skate shoe comes in a black canvas and leather upper, with artwork from the album cover on the sides. The album artwork captures the Hindenburg airship disaster, and this shoe pays tribute to that with its own unique style. The 50th Anniversary capsule collection also includes apparel, so you can rock the Led Zeppelin look from head to toe.

title: Vans Led Zeppelin x Era '50th Anniversary'  VN0A38FRT5Z
description: February 2019 marked the 50th anniversary of Led Zeppelin's self-titled debut album, and to celebrate, Vans created a special capsule collection honoring the legendary band. The highlight of the collection is the Led Zeppelin x Era '50th Anniversary' shoes, which feature a black leather upper with band symbols in white throughout. These shoes are a must-have for any fan of Led Zeppelin or Vans, and they're sure to become one of your favorite pairs in your rotation.

description: The Fear of God x Era 95 DX 'Collection 2 Red' from renowned designer Jerry Lorenzo and iconic sneaker brand Vans is a must-have for any sneakerhead's collection. This limited edition sneaker features black-and-white branding on the body with red corduroy overlays at the forefoot and heel, adding texture and dimension to the classic silhouette. The shoe sits atop a gum-rubber sole, providing sticky traction and a comfortable ride

title: Vans Fear of God x Slip-On 47 DX 'Collection 2 Red'  VN0A3J9FPQT
description: The Vans Fear of God x Slip-On 47 DX 'Collection 2 Red' was released as part of Vans' second collection with Jerry Lorenzo's Fear of God. The shoe features a black canvas upper stamped with white 'Fear of God' branding and red suede overlays on the toe and heel. A padded ankle collar, 'FOG' branding under the tongue, a white waffle rubber outsole and ‘Off the Wall’ branding on the heel complete the look. This shoe is perfect for anyone who loves clean lines and a minimalistic aesthetic.

title: Vans Opening Ceremony x Old Skool LX 'Glitter Pack'  VN000VOJPZL
description: Introducing the Vans Opening Ceremony x Old Skool LX 'Glitter Pack'! This sneaker is rendered with an all-over glitter application in a tonal teal hue, making it perfect for those who love to stand out. Fashioned with leather paneling on the upper, the sneaker also showcases the signature jazz-stripe and waffle outsole as a nod to the sneaker’s original design.

title: Vans Opening Ceremony x Old Skool LX 'Glitter Pack'  VN000VOJPZK
description: Vans Opening Ceremony x Old Skool LX 'Glitter Pack' is sure to make you stand out from the crowd with its glittery Lavender Pink finish and contrasting red jazz stripe. The leather sock liner also has a shiny finish for an extra touch of luxury. But don't worry, the vulcanized midsole and waffle traction pattern keeps the signature look intact. So whether you're dressing up for a special occasion or just wanting to add a little sparkle to your everyday look, this sneaker is perfect for you!

title: Vans WTAPS x Authentic Syndicate 'Wings'  VN000EFPGWE
description: When it comes to cool, trendy footwear, it doesn't get much better than the Vans WTAPS x Authentic Syndicate 'Wings' shoes. These limited edition kicks come in a beautiful golden hue, with W)TAPS logos appearing around the collar. They're perfect for making a statement, whether you're hitting the streets or the skate park. The high-quality suede upper and UltraCush HD insole provide both style and comfort, while the heightened midsole foxing completes the classic look.

title: Vans Takashi Murakami Slip-On LX ' Skull'  VN-0ZSIGUI
description: Takashi Murakami is a world-renowned Japanese artist who is known for his bright and vibrant colors, as well as his anime and Japanese pop culture influences. The Takashi Murakami Slip-On LX 'Yellow Skull' celebrates his creativity with a canvas upper covered in skull prints, evocative of motifs in his other work. This low-top sneaker also features a classic Vans Slip-On design and a vulcanized sole, making it both stylish and comfortable. The sneaker was released alongside three similarly themed t-shirts, so you can complete the look.

title: Vans The North Face x SK8-HI 46 MTE DX 'Red'  VN0A3DQ5QWS
description: Introducing the Vans The North Face x Sk8Hi 46 MTE DX sneaker, the perfect footwear for those cold weather adventures. This high-top sneaker features a weather-resistant black suede upper with red laminate ballistic nylon overlays, making it equipped to handle anything nature throws your way. The UltraCush sockliners and MTE 360 technology work together to keep your feet warm and dry all day long, while the vulcanized lug outsole provides optimal traction on slippery surfaces. Available in multiple colors, the Vans The North Face x Sk8Hi 46 MTE DX sneaker is sure to become your go-to footwear for all those cold weather excursions.

The vulcanized rubber midsole and gum rubber outsole provide great comfort and durability, making this an ideal sneaker for everyday wear.

title: Vans Andres Serrano x Supreme x SK8-HI 'Blood and Semen'  VN0A347TRZW
description: The Vans Andres Serrano x Supreme x Sk8-Hi 'Blood and Semen' is a must-have for any Supreme or Vans fan. The shoe is constructed from high-quality materials, with black suede on the toe, eyelets, heel, and a white Jazz stripe. This is a limited-edition shoe that is sure to turn heads, so don't miss your chance to own a piece of history.

title: Vans Andres Serrano x Supreme x Old Skool 'Blood and Semen'  VN000ZD4RZW
description: The 'Blood and Semen' Old Skool is a special colorway of the classic Vans sneaker that was released in September 2017 in collaboration with Supreme and artist Andres Serrano. The shoe features Serrano's iconic 'Blood and Semen' artwork on the side panels, with a white Jazz Stripe and black suede on the toe, eyelets, and heel. This limited-edition sneaker is perfect for anyone who loves Supreme, Vans, or unique and stylish sneakers.

title: Vans Thrasher x Slip-On Pro 'Thrasher'  VN0A347VOTE
description: Vans and Thrasher teamed up for a collaboration that is sure to get skateboarders psyched. The Vans Thrasher x Slip-On Pro combines the best of both brands, with Vans' UltraCush technology and the iconic Thrasher logo. This shoe is perfect for hitting the skatepark or just cruising around town. The black canvas upper is accented by the red foxing stripe and the Thrasher logo on the toe. Whether you're a seasoned skater or a beginner, the Vans Thrasher x Slip-On Pro is a great choice.

description: The Vans Old Skool 'Madder' shoe is a classic skate silhouette with a modern twist. The suede and mesh construction provides durability and breathability, while the Madder Brown hues add a unique touch of style. The padded heel collar protects your feet while skating, and the waffle outsole provides optimal traction.

title: Vans Old Skool 'Black Checkerboard'  VN0A38G1P0S
description: The all-new Vans Old Skool 'Black Checkerboard' is what you need in your life this season! The signature waffle outsole provides superior comfort and traction, making these perfect for all-day wear. Add a touch of vintage style to your wardrobe with the Vans Old Skool 'Black Checkerboard'.

title: Vans Bodega x Half Cab LX 'Return of the Dragon'  VN0A3A76NSA
description: Bodega and Vans have partnered up to bring you an exclusive colorway of the Half Cab LX sneaker. For added comfort, the sneaker has a padded collar and chunky gum sole unit. This is a must-have for any serious sneaker head or fashion enthusiast.

Charlie Brown's iconic catchphrase is featured on the tongues, adding a fun pop of personality to this otherwise classic sneaker.

description: The NEIGHBORHOOD x Mister Cartoon x Vans Old Skool 36 DX ‘Tokyo Los Angeles’ is the perfect blend of East meets West. This limited edition sneaker is a tribute to the two cities that have been integral to the brand's DNA. The monochromatic black suede upper with tonal leather side stripes and custom ‘Tokyo’ and ‘Los Angeles’ embroidery on the toe box of the right and left shoe give this shoe a clean look that is sure to turn heads. On the back, ‘Uncle Toons Mart’ and ‘By NEIGHBORHOOD’ adorns each heel panel, adding a touch of fun.

This limited edition sneaker is a tribute to the two cities that have been integral to the brand's DNA. The monochromatic black suede upper with tonal leather side stripes and custom ‘Tokyo’ and ‘Los Angeles’ embroidery on the toe box of the right and left shoe give this shoe a clean look that is sure to turn heads. On the back, ‘Uncle Toons Mart’ and ‘By NEIGHBORHOOD’ adorns each heel panel, adding a touch of fun.

description: In celebration of Ronnie Fieg's 10th anniversary, Kith has teamed up with Vans to release a special edition capsule collection. The Kith x Vans Vault OG Classic Slip-On LX 'Gray Tile' is a must-have for any sneakerhead or fashion enthusiast. The unique all-over print on the canvas upper is eye-catching and sure to turn heads. The comfortable fit and easy on/off design make the shoes perfect for everyday wear. The red license plate at the heel is a nice pop of color that adds a bit of contrast to the overall look. The Vans branding on the sockliner and the anniversary-themed 'KXTH' logo complete the design of these special edition shoes.

title: Vans Kith x Vault OG Classic Slip-On LX 'Multi Tile'  VN0A45JK6BR
description: Ronnie Fieg’s highly anticipated 10th anniversary collection with Vans Vault is finally here, and it does not disappoint. The Kith x Vans Vault OG Classic Slip-On LX ‘Multi Tile’ is a standout from the collection, with its eye-catching canvas upper covered in a series of abstract geometric prints. traditional Vans logo tab adorns the lateral side, but with mismatched branding on the interior side for a fun twist. Underfoot, you’ll find Vans’ signature waffle-traction outsole in tacky gum rubber – perfect for keeping you grounded whether you’re hitting the streets or the skate park.

title: Vans Kith x Vault OG Classic Slip-On LX 'Floral'  VN0A45JK6BZ
description: To celebrate its 10th anniversary, New York-based retailer Kith has teamed up with Vans Vault on a special capsule collection. The Vans Kith x Vault by Slip-On OG Classic is a striking sneaker that features an eye-catching floral design. The shoes are crafted from a durable canvas material and rest on a comfortable rubber sole, making them ideal for everyday wear. The sockliner isbranded with Vans logos and the commemorative ‘KXTH’ logo, adding a stylish finishing touch to this must-have shoe.

title: Vans Kith x Vault OG Classic Slip-On 'Multi Tile'  VN0A4BUZ6BR
description: In celebration of their 10-year anniversary, New York-based retailer Kith has teamed up with Vans Vault to release an expansive collection of Slip-Ons. This 'Multi Tile' colorway is one of the most eye-catching in the bunch, with a subtle multicolor print applied to the canvas upper. Elastic gore detailing and a woven Vans tab on the lateral side add some nice finishing touches, while a contrasting white midsole provides a contrast against the colorful upper. A standard waffle traction outsole in grippy gum rubber completes the look.

title: Vans Kith x Vault OG Classic Slip-On 'Bandana Multi'  VN0A4BUZ6CJ
description: The Vans Vault Classic Slip-On x Kith TD is a special edition shoe from the 10-year anniversary collection of Ronnie Fieg's retail empire and brand. This shoe features a multicolor bandana print on the canvas upper, with elastic gore detailing for easy on and off. The sockliner includes traditional Vans branding, as well as a special 'KXTH' logo. The low-top is mounted on a vulcanized rubber midsole, and the outsole features a waffle-tread gum rubber for added support and traction.
